20 DOCUMENTATION DURING SUPPLY EXECUTION 
VENDOR  shall supply as minimum all the documentation listed under the Attachment 2. VENDOR  
is responsible to supply/submit the required documentation in accordance with the agreed 
schedule as per Attachment 2. 
Documentation shall be in accordance with the Project specification number 4503-YZ-PC-
T0000003 (SLN-2725-0000-00-Z-0003) “VENDOR DOCUMENT CONTROL PROCEDURE” . 
The CONTRACTOR  will return the submitted documentation for review/approval within fifteen (15) 
working days from the receipt. 
All documentation returned to the VENDOR  with comments shall be resubmitted to the 
CONTRACTOR  within ten (10) working days from the receipt. 
The CONTRACTOR  review /approval do not relieve the VENDOR  from his responsibilities to 
comply with the contractual obligation. 
For the Final documentation, VENDOR  shall follow the Project specification number  4503-YZ-PC-
T0000003 (SLN-2725-0000-00-Z-0003) “VENDOR DOCUMENT CONTROL PROCEDURE”  for the 
detail criteria/guidelines for arranging the documentation inside the Final Data Books. Four (4) soft 
copies (CD) are required for final data books (TO BE CONFIRMED).

